{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_51_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 サプライズ・パンケーキ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――誕生日当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio's Birthday",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、OKが出るとは思わなかったわ\n莉央さんが出る番組に、私達が急にサプライズ出演って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought they would agree to this.\nHaving us suddenly make a surprise appearance on a show Rio-san is on",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5333333214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.3544211268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "番組的に盛り上がると思ったんじゃない？\nそれに、莉央も喜ぶだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They probably thought it would liven up the show‚right?\nBesides‚Rio will be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9540819684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "特別コーナーも作ってもらったんだ。失敗は出来ないよ\n今は、間に合うように完成させることだけ考えよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They even made a special section for us. We can't fail.\nLet's just focus on finishing it on time for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6000006993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.793129146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。私はいつでも始められるわ\n今日のために、レシピも読み込んできたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. I'm ready to start whenever.\nI've studied the recipe for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8231984337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.4218140482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいことこの上ないね\n……怜。オフなのに、出てくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't ask for anything more reliable.\n…Rei‚thanks for coming out‚even though it's your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0000006993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8567572156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。何、改まって。乗りかかった船だもの\n最後までやりきるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. What are you being so formal for? I'm already on board.\nI'll see it through to the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6637201827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.697053516
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　もうすぐコーナーが始まるわよ！\n間に合うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! The section is about to start!\nAre we going to make it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.897053516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4097725271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "怜が生地を焦がさなかったら\nもう少し早く出来てたんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Rei hadn't burnt the dough‚\nwe would've been done a little earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4666688919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0146947581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かにそうかもしれないけど\n葵も無駄に踊りながらクリームを泡立ててたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That might be true‚\nbut you were also whipping the cream while dancing unnecessarily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3475559117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.7857628226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あれは気持ちを込めてたんだよ\nターンするのとしないのでは味が変わるからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was putting my heart into it.\nThe taste changes depending on whether you do a turn or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2666724523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9524282812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、僕等のコーナーを後ろにずらしてもらおう\nちょっと頼んでくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚let's ask them to postpone our section.\nI'll go ask them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4000047684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "頼んでくるって、そんなことして大丈夫なの？\n収録も進んでるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're going to ask them? Is that really okay?\nThey're already in the middle of recording…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.325380568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.8539262175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "後で{user}君に\n怒られるかもしれないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might get scolded\nby {user}-san later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3333396276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3472594936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日の主役に未完成のパンケーキを\n出す訳にはいかない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't give the star of the show\nan unfinished pancake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9000062943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6115221063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。それなら、私が話してくる\n葵はパンケーキをお願い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I'll go talk to them.\nAoi‚you focus on the pancakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2274685744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.4748552679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "それがいいね。怜にパンケーキを任せたら\n日付が変わってしまうかもしれないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a good idea. If I left the pancakes to Rei‚\nit might be tomorrow by the time we're done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9000057857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.3965104777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでかかんないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It won't take that long!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3965104777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.313177192
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.313177192
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.533337911
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.1965206979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……\nありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff… Huff…\nThank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0147124812,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.6636267000003,
          "startTime": 132.6813761079
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.6813761079
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.6502208112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　葵、怜……？　なんでここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm? Aoi‚Rei…? Why are you here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6502208112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.1653030911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "僕達、どうしても莉央に会いたくて\n今日は何の日だと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We really wanted to see you‚Rio.\nDo you know what day it is today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5666826249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの誕生日ですよね！\nスペシャルコーナーを用意していただきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Rio-san's birthday!\nWe have a special section prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.270677428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.0549370167
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
